Thomas E. Polen Jr.President, Becton, Dickinson and CompanyAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 0 Board Members in 0 different organizations across 2 different industries.44$3,260,857As of Fiscal Year 2016
Background

		Mr. Thomas E. Polen, Jr., has been President of Becton, Dickinson and Company since April 23, 2017. Mr. Polen has been the President at CareFusion Corporation since March 17, 2015. He served as Executive Vice President and President of Medical Segment at Becton, Dickinson and Company from October 01, 2014 to April 23, 2017. Mr. Polen served as the Segment President of BD Medical at Becton, Dickinson and Company.	
	



