Polen has served as the President of Becton, Dickinson since April 2017. Most recently he was Executive Vice President and President of Medical Segment at the company. Polen earned his BS degree from the University of Maryland and worked at Johns Hopkins Hospital before joining a startup based in  
Personal Attributes and Interests

